    "description": "General Packer Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells various packaging machines and peripheral equipment, and food processing and confectionery production machinery in Japan and internationally. It provides pouch filling-sealing machines, automatic bag forming and filling-sealing machines, automatic N2 gas flushing filling-sealing machines, and special type automatics bag filling-sealing machines, as well as automatic tray and desiccant insert bag feeding packaging machines, non-instructive residual oxygen analyzers, and chocolate manufacturing machines. The company also offers flour packaging, pasta packaging, drip coffee packaging, rice packaging, stick packages outer packaging, intravenous solution bag packaging, ampoule filling gas substitution packaging, medical device packaging, health foods packaging, pet foods packaging, and seed and seedling packaging system. The company was founded in 1961 and is headquartered in Kitanagoya, Japan."
